Base-year net number of migrants by age, sex, and education;
The transition between education categories. This input is specific to multi-state population projections. It is the age-specific probabilities for young men or women to move, e.g. from the category of primary educational attainment to secondary attainment.  The data needed for the calculation of precise transition rates is not readily available, thus transition rates were approximated from the educational attainment at each age and level.

